Package TicTac4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigBoard
    This is the only JFrame for Tic-Tac-4.
    BoardPanel
    This class holds the code needed to create each Connect-4 game.
    Main
    This project was created for fun, and a challenge related to coding a set of JPanels in a grid layout within one JFrame.
    Piece
    This class extends a regular JComponent, styled as an outer rectangle used as a border, and an inner oval used as the Connect-4 game piece.
